9.1.0 08/01//2017

Many changes in regard to the right-mouse-click (context menu) for desktop, file manager, file, folder
open file, open directory, compress ...
Many new links were necessary to have the same type of folder that was selected. They inherited folders from other icon theme.
Enough changes to up the number to 9.1.0

Linux Mint 18.1 Cinnamon, Mate and Xfce seems to be in order for 100%.


