9.0.3 06/01/2017

Something was 'off' with the mintupdate icons. They appeared normal and then to big... An arc theme or mint-y themes issue A cinnamon issue
tried to fix it by making all icons smaller from 24 to 16 px
It was an ugly sight - new version and hope it is solved.

Think I found the culprit (or another culprit) Sardi Mono Numix had icons from Numix that were too big. Same version reload. Deleted 4 icons


