8.5.0 30/01/2017

Recording every step can even take longer as actually doing it.

- ran a script to eleminate empty <text ... </text> in all svg another 3MB profit

		sed -i '/<text/,/<\/text>/d' "$1"
- some of the icons still have big size - due to incredible amount of data for shade
- some icons will have no shade for that reason  - to do make the shades again
- rewrite of scripts of all icon themes - more explanation and uniformity over all themes
- all scripts have been tested and result is on github sardi-extra
- new scripts for new icon themes luv and paper


