svgcleaner action on Sardi Mono Numix Colora
------------------------------
Sardi Mono Numix Colora before
	559 KB
Sardi Mono Numix Colora after
	177 KB
------------------------------




svgcleaner action on Sardi Mono Numix
------------------------------
Sardi Mono Numix before
	493 KB
Sardi Mono Numix after
	125 KB
------------------------------



svgcleaner action on Sardi Mono Mint-X-Grey
------------------------------
Sardi Mono Mint-X-Grey before
	4 MB
Sardi  Mono Mint-X-Grey after
	941 KB
------------------------------



svgcleaner action on Sardi Mono Vertexed
------------------------------
Sardi Mono Vertexed before
	2.2 MB
Sardi Mono Vertexed after
	849 KB
------------------------------


svgcleaner action on Flexible Arc
------------------------------
Sardi Flexible Arc before
	544,4 KB
Sardi Flexible Arc after
	312 KB
------------------------------

Moved Sardi Mono Arc to Sardi Extra


8.2.0 27/12/2016


Sardi Breeze Dark has moved to Sardi Extra.

Sardi Arc has moved to Sardi Extra.

Sardi Colora/Places has received flat looking icons from Sardi/Places and made orange for scripting.

Sardi/scalable/places has received all icons from Sardi Flat/scalable/places. No more shade in folders.

Sardi Flat has received all mimetypes from Numix


Comparison between Sardi Mono apps and Sardi Flat apps
Sardi Flat icons added from Sardi Mono  57a1cfff

database-chakra
document-preview
document-save-delete
gtk-connect
all symbolic or tray icons like spotify, inkscape etc...

worked with blend to figure out differences between 4 icon themes
not all recorded

Comparison between Sardi Mono apps and Sardi apps
Sardi icons added from Sardi Mono  57a1cfff

database-chakra
document-preview
document-save
gtk-connect
nm-signal etc... all gone
security-low and -medium gone


Sardi Mono icons added from Sardi

not recorded




