			system_section
	scalable devices
		lots of broken icons - deleted broken onces and copied rest
	scalable emblems
		all broken no copy/paste
	scalable mimetypes
		lots of broken icons - deleted broken onces and copied rest
	scalable panel
		copy/paste all
	scalable places
		lots of broken icons - deleted broken onces and copied rest
	scalable status
		lots of broken icons - deleted broken onces and copied rest









